                  Tickle has a shell-based environment,
                  the commands are the following:

                @{" Send92      " link      U_SEND} - Sends files to the TI-92.
                @{" Recv92      " link      U_RECV} - Receives files from the TI-92.
                @{" CaptRom92   " link   U_CAPTROM} - Captures the TI-92's ROM.
                @{" Remote92    " link    U_REMOTE} - Remote-control the TI-92.
                @{" FLink       " link       FLINK} - Fargo linker.
