                                  @{b}@{u}FUTURE@{uu}@{ub}


So, any plans for the future of Tickle92? Perhaps:

    o A GUI, if anyone comes up with a good reason why, the only
      reason we would make a GUI for is to avoid all those nasty
      second-hand GUIs that appear on AmiNet. =) Just kidding, feel free
      to make a GUI if you like.

    o A distant voice in says that we should turn Tickle92 into a device,
      so that you would be able to use the functions of Tickle from
      other software.

    o Improve on Remote92.

The future depends mostly on user-response however, so if you have
anything you would like to say to us, do it!

Please read the @{"contacts page" link CONTACT} to find out how to contact us.

@endnode
